title: Can't reply on forums must be Level 5
body: Says I can't reply on forum posts but my account is level 23 I'm confused.

replies.body:
Sometimes your Boards and Summoner profiles fall out of sync. Typically a post such as this will force a sync between the two, which appears to be what happened. I see you as level 24 on your boards profile, so you should not see any issues posting now. 

Let me know if you have any questions.
